Install Notes For Grypt
=======================

Unpack the source to the directory:

	purple-$VERSION/gtk/plugins/grypt

Apply the file named `patch' outside the main Purple source root:

	$ patch < purple-$VERSION/gtk/plugins/grypt/patch

Then proceed to run the Purple usual installation process:

	./configure
	make && make install

Usage Notes
===========

Exchange keys with buddies using "gpg --import/export"
and use "gpg --edit-key" with the "trust" command to
set the trust levels on the keys to level 5.
